1. When a user presses mouse click down in canvas area send an emit called 
'mouse_down' and send with it the 
	a. user id
	b. x and y coord

2. 'mouse_down' listener checks to see if global variable 'free_canvas' is set to true. If true set the 'drawer_id' = the user id and set 'free_canvas' = false. and 


send a emit stating which user (by socket.id) is clicking down and and turn is free_canvas to false.
2. When a mouse up from the same user occurs, turn the free_canvas to true. This allows the another use to draw

3. users is an array of socket Ids



